# Next.js Architecture

Follow the slim starter layout:

- **Features** → `src/features/{name}/` (see `.agents/feature-structure.md`)
- **Services** → `src/services/{domain}/` when calling APIs (see `.agents/service-structure.md`)
- **Components** → `ui/` (shadcn), `shared/` (cross-feature), or feature-scoped
- **Naming** → `.agents/naming-conventions.md`

Do not put business logic in route files. Do not create parallel folder structures.
